{"tid":506440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄺保羅聖誕文告希望市民盡力關懷照顧有困難的人和守望相助","createTime":"2017-12-22T08:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T05:54:04.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"600023e32b5d9cc5689eea955da9444e7a0a6cce","tid":506440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"香港聖公會大主教鄺保羅發表聖誕文告, 他說特區政府最近公布的貧窮人口創新口, 貧窮和人口老化是兩個連緊扣的難題, 要戰勝這一場仗, 需要全港市民的毅力和努力, 政府一方面要訂定創新和有前瞻性的政策去回應. 他希望每一位市民, 發揮聖誕的施予精神, 盡力關懷照顧有困難的人及守望相助.<br />\n<br />\n鄺保羅說市民要慶祝一個有意義的聖誕, 就是要學效耶穌一樣關懷其他人. 他表示有廣告鼓勵大家在慶祝聖誕節時, 盡量狂歡和消費, 但聖誕節的核心精神, 是在於「施予 」和「分享 」, 除了物質的供應之外, 一句簡單的噓寒問暖, 也可能會帶來奇蹟.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171222120906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20171222120906&d=c9o%2Bp0wmVt%2Bykjwp0NVuh8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c21463cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171222120906</a>"},{"pid":"1d1e63c6b891e94d7abf836bda780a8d6791dcc3","tid":506440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f269929a21a24a9397afe302786f2b074f5431b7","tid":506440,"uid":124991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"不要以為我來是帶和平到世上來的；我並沒有帶來和平，而是帶來刀劍。"},{"pid":"489c31b6f8461b756a0d4e92a123df701f68e82a","tid":506440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f269929a21a24a9397afe302786f2b074f5431b7","tid":506440,"uid":124991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"不要以為我來是帶和平到世上來的；我並沒有帶來和平，而是帶來刀劍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f992a6d89dbcd72427fbf60beed0b7568ee58255","tid":506440,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-